text: Kyzylkuper () is a rural locality (a village) in Gorkovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 82 as of 2010. There is 1 streets. == Geography == It is located 29 km from Kushnarenkovo, 3 km from Ilikovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Kyzylkuper
